title: 167. Andy & DJ CTI: False Accusations, Loser Shit & Draining The Swamp Ft. Billy Prempeh
itunes:title: 167. Andy & DJ CTI: False Accusations, Loser Shit & Draining The Swamp Ft. Billy Prempeh
description: Just because you don't like the information doesn't mean it's not true. In today's episode, Andy and the crew are joined by Billy Prempeh. They discuss how false accusations similar to what's happening to Dave Portnoy minimize the actual victims of rape, how the society has grown soft to winning, and the Russian informant arrested for lying to the FBI in the Steele dossier.
